<div class="container tablet-width">

  <hgroup>
    <h1>npm Enterprise</h1>
    <h2>Licensing</h2>
  </hgroup>

  <section>
    <h2>Step 1: confirm your email address</h2>
    <p>Thanks for choosing to license npm Enterprise. To get started, enter the email address you
      wish to use for billing.</p>
    <p>If you have previously signed up for a trial and have your license key handy, you can enter
      it now to go straight to the next step.</p>
    <p>If you don't enter a license key, we will email you a link to the next step.</p>

    <form method="post">
      Billing email: <input type="text" name="email" placeholder="billing@mycompany.com"><br>
      License key (optional): <input type="text" name="license" placeholder="aaaaaaaa-bbbb-cccc-dddd-eeeeeeeeeeee">
      <input type="submit" class="full-width" value="Verify billing email">
      {{> form_security}}
    </form>
  </section>

</div>
